  "legal": {
    "privacyHtml": "<h2>Privacy Policy</h2><p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 1, 2026</p><p>Saigon Rider (\"the App\") is operated by WellConn Co., Ltd. (\"we\"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal data you share with us.</p><h2>1. Data We Collect</h2><ul><li><strong>Account info:</strong> phone number, nickname, rider style</li><li><strong>Location data:</strong> GPS coordinates during rides (only while the app is in use)</li><li><strong>Usage data:</strong> quest progress, ride history, in-app purchases</li><li><strong>Device info:</strong> device UUID, OS version, FCM token</li></ul><h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2><ul><li>Provide and improve ride tracking, quests, and rewards</li><li>Send push notifications you opted in to</li><li>Analyze aggregated usage patterns (no individual profiling)</li></ul><h2>3. Data Sharing</h2><p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share limited data with:</p><ul><li>Cloud infrastructure providers (hosting)</li><li>Push notification services (Firebase)</li></ul><h2>4. Data Retention</h2><p>We retain your data while your account is active. Upon account deletion, all personal data is permanently removed within 30 days.</p><h2>5. Your Rights</h2><ul><li>Access and download your data (Settings → Account)</li><li>Delete your account and all associated data</li><li>Withdraw consent for location or notifications at any time</li></ul><h2>6. Contact</h2><p>For privacy inquiries, use the in-app Support or email us at support@sgr.com.</p>",
    "termsHtml": "<h2>Terms of Service</h2><p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> June 1, 2026</p><p>By using Saigon Rider (\"the App\"), you agree to these Terms of Service.</p><h2>1. Eligibility</h2><p>You must be at least 14 years old to use the App. By registering, you confirm you meet this age requirement.</p><h2>2. Account</h2><ul><li>One account per phone number</li><li>You are responsible for keeping your login credentials secure</li><li>We may suspend accounts that violate these terms</li></ul><h2>3. Virtual Currency & Items</h2><ul><li>Gold, XP, badges, and items are virtual and have no real-world monetary value</li><li>Virtual items cannot be transferred, sold, or exchanged for cash</li><li>We reserve the right to modify item values and availability</li></ul><h2>4. Acceptable Use</h2><p>You agree not to:</p><ul><li>Use GPS spoofing or other location manipulation</li><li>Exploit bugs or use automated tools</li><li>Post offensive or illegal content in feeds or messages</li></ul><h2>5. Ride Safety</h2><p>The App is a gamified companion — always follow traffic laws. We are not liable for accidents during rides.</p><h2>6. Termination</h2><p>You may delete your account at any time. We may terminate accounts for violations without prior notice.</p><h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2><p>The App is provided \"as is\". We are not liable for service interruptions, data loss, or damages arising from use of the App.</p><h2>8. Changes</h2><p>We may update these terms. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p><h2>9. Contact</h2><p>Questions about these terms? Use in-app Support or email support@sgr.com.</p>"
  },
